sentences: Tom Carolan (born March 2, 1961) is an American music executive and entrepreneur.
In 2004, Carolan founded J Rae Entertainment, named after his daughter Juliana Rae Carolan.
In 2007 Carolan folded J Rae Entertainment into Total Live Music, of which he is founder and president.
Its work over the years includes assisting Coachella Music Festival and Mile High Music Festival in capturing and streaming performances to the AT&T Blueroom.
